{"tid":1771922,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持本土港產片] 鄧麗欣再度衝擊影后《金都》 My Prince Edward 預告","createTime":"2019-12-06T07:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:35:53.000Z","uid":15213,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e65a0bfe30283d9f83b9b929bde807eb195a6b7","tid":1771922,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DMUYt9i8V9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDMUYt9i8V9s&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScPkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=2d44dd7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DMUYt9i8V9s</a><br />\n<br />\n「婚姻」一直被描繪為愛情的大團圓結局，三十開外的女性除了結婚生子，似乎沒有出路。電影以太子的平民化婚慶聖地金都商場為背景，三十多歲的婚紗店員為了應付男友催婚，逼於處理早年為錢假結婚的爛攤子。每天都離不開婚嫁話題的她，如何選擇自己的人生路向？ <br />\n<br />\n⭐️榮獲 金馬影展與亞洲電影促進聯盟頒發「NETPAC奈派克獎」 ⭐️<br />\n⭐️本屆金馬獎三項提名 最佳男主角 最佳新導演 最佳原創電影歌曲⭐️<br />\n⭐️2019年香港亞洲電影節HKAFF 閉幕電影⭐️<br />\n⭐️第四屆「首部劇情電影計劃」大專組得獎作品⭐️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演/編劇：黃綺琳 (瑪嘉烈與大衛）<br />\n<br />\n演員：鄧麗欣 朱栢康 鮑起靜 金楷杰 林二汶 許素瑩 岑珈其<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前亞洲電影節首映咗<br />\n睇過可以細藍字劇透討論下"},{"pid":"bd29190d524b11ffd18b791bcc08412f1675c27a","tid":1771922,"uid":15213,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtxDzHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtxDzHT.jpg&h=8712ca98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67bc5d683774bb22ae01b3c652a0817aa8f2d192","tid":1771922,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"仲有邊間戲院唔係紅底黑底？"},{"pid":"d5bb75031d65179575d00d939f134160977820bf","tid":1771922,"uid":206762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:32:39.000Z","msg":"巴打洗唔洗咁早開定po呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚上個陣冇人記得呢個po"},{"pid":"647c31d1b85a7484aab61842d8a2a677f726a82b","tid":1771922,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-1